::Astral/The Galactors/Greven::

Astral was hit by the air shots, blowing him out of the way of the saw
blades. He fires two missiles at Triggerhappy, gaining altitude.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Supernova/Slasys/Scrap jet avoids the fireball, recieving Zardus's
orders and firing twenty laser shots at Unicron.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Vycir/Flare jet detects Cutthroat falling to the ground, and fires
one more grenade at him before pulling up.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Greven looks around for a target, seeing Surgital. He smiles. Finally
some fighting. He charges the large robot, firing two missiles from
each missile launcher at him, four in all heading toward Surgital's
back.


--- In nbwrpg@y..., "LurkerAbyss" <1641coburn@h...> wrote:
> ::Triggerhappy/Surgital/Cutthroat::
> 
>         Triggerhappy did multiple backflips and dodged the
missiles.  He fired 2 shots from his compressed air cannon up at
Astral.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>         Surgital was hit by all the missiles, and fell to the
ground.  He got up on his feet, and he was enraged.
> 
>          "I must squash you all, you little flies!" Surgital yelled.
> 
>         Both of his hands reverted into round, saw-blades.  Then, he
shot both of the blades at Astral.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>          Cutthroat tried to fly away from the missiles and
grenades.  The missiles hit his wings, and sent him falling to the
ground.  He got up, then shot a fireball from his mouth up at the
Supernova/Slasys/Scrap jet.
